## Architecture

```
GitLab Webhook (MR opened)
        │
        ▼
┌─────────────────┐
│   FastAPI App   │  ← main.py
│                 │
│  /webhook       │  Receives MR events
│  /analyze       │  Blast radius for dashboard
│  /graph         │  Full project dependency graph
│  /describe      │  Claude file descriptions
│  /chat          │  Codebase Q&A
└────────┬────────┘
         │
    ┌────┴────┐
    │         │
    ▼         ▼
GitLab    GitLab
REST API  Orbit API
(MR diff) (Graph traversal)
    │         │
    └────┬────┘
         │
         ▼
  ┌─────────────┐
  │   Claude    │  Synthesizes analysis
  │ Sonnet 4.6  │  Generates MR comment
  └─────────────┘
         │
         ▼
  MR Comment Posted
```

