## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Backend | FastAPI + Uvicorn |
| Graph queries | GitLab Orbit API |
| MR data | GitLab REST API |
| AI synthesis | Claude Sonnet 4.6 (Anthropic) |
| Deployment | Railway (Docker) |

